		<h2>Who We Are</h2>
	
		<img class="hr_breaks" src="img/hr-black.png" />
		
		<div style="clear: both;">
		
		<img style="float: right; margin: 0px 0px 15px 25px; width: 450px;" src="img/anglo-pumps-image-20150313_095908.jpg" />
	
		<p>Our head quarters are based in Bedford with office and factory space covering 9000 square feet. We offer a comprehensive service including assessing site viability, design, sizing selecting and installing equipment. The company offers services through out the UK and select equipment from a wide range of manufactures, tailoring the equipment to suit the individual requirements.</p>

		<p>We undertake complete project managing, station design, equipment selection and programming, including any civil engineering needs. Anglo offer a range of maintenance products to ensure the reliability and operation efficiency of pumping systems and associated equipment.</p>
	
		<p>Our engineers are fully trained with confined space procedures and all relevant 	health and safety issues and have many years of experience. At our headquarters we have a fully-equipped workshop staffed by experts, offering total in house service to support our maintenance activities. We understand our customers demand a round the clock service 24 hours, 7 days a week 365 days a year. We pride ourselves for offering this service.</p>
		
		<div style="clear: both;"></div>
		
